{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HBZHGQGH3sGDDpwxcnvttP","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Workspace Agent Design Document\n     2→\n     3→## Overview\n     4→\n     5→Design for a new **Workspace Agent** within OfficeAgent infrastructure. Handles workspace creation requests from AugLoop while maintaining complete isolation from CreateAgent document generation flow.\n     6→\n     7→The Workspace Agent generates **Office artifacts** including:\n     8→- **Reports** - Business reports, analysis summaries, executive briefings\n     9→- **Documents** - Word documents, memos, proposals\n    10→- **Presentations** - PowerPoint decks, pitch decks, training materials\n    11→- **Newsletters** - Internal communications, team updates\n    12→- **Blogs** - Blog posts, articles, thought leadership content\n    13→\n    14→The agent uses a **two-phase sub-agent architecture**:\n    15→1. **Planning Phase** (`@workspace-planner`) - Analyzes user intent, researches content, generates structured outline\n    16→2. **Generation Phase** (`@workspace-generator`) - Executes plan, generates artifact content\n    17→\n    18→## Architecture\n    19→\n    20→### Infrastructure Overview\n    21→\n    22→| Directory | Purpose |\n    23→|-----------|---------|\n    24→| `modules/api/` | Express server, WebSocket handling |\n    25→| `modules/core/` | BaseAgent, logging, WebSocket router |\n    26→| `modules/grounding/` | Enterprise search, image search, parsing |\n    27→| `modules/message-protocol/` | Message types, request/response structures |\n    28→| `agents/` | Individual agent implementations |\n    29→\n    30→### Workspace Agent Structure\n    31→\n    32→```\n    33→agents/workspace-agent/\n    34→├── src/\n    35→│   ├── index.ts\n    36→│   ├── workspace-agent.ts        # Main orchestrator (extends BaseAgent)\n    37→│   ├── registry.ts               # AgentRegistryConfig\n    38→│   ├── types.ts                  # Internal types\n    39→│   ├── utils.ts                  # Helpers (buildResponsePayload, sendWebSocketResponse)\n    40→│   │\n    41→│   ├── hooks/\n    42→│   │   ├── index.ts              # Hook exports\n    43→│   │   └── stage-hooks.ts        # PostToolUse hook for incremental responses\n    44→│   │\n    45→│   ├── skills/\n    46→│   │   └── workspace-setup/\n    47→│   │       ├── skill.md          # Main skill entry point\n    48→│   │       └── workflow_steps/\n    49→│   │           └── WORKFLOW.md   # Orchestration workflow\n    50→│   │\n    51→│   ├── subagents/\n    52→│   │   ├── workspace-planner.md  # Phase 1: Planning sub-agent\n    53→│   │   └── workspace-generator.md # Phase 2: Generation sub-agent\n    54→│   │\n    55→│   └── prompts/\n    56→│       └── system-prompt.md      # Orchestrator instructions\n    57→│\n    58→├── tests/\n    59→├── package.json\n    60→└── tsconfig.json\n    61→```\n    62→\n    63→### Existing Agents (Reference)\n    64→\n    65→| Agent ID | Message Type | Reference |\n    66→|----------|--------------|-----------|\n    67→| `create-agent` | `chat_request` | [agents/create-agent/src/create-agent.ts](../agents/create-agent/src/create-agent.ts) |\n    68→| `dw-paralegal-agent` | `paralegal_agent_request` | [agents/dw-paralegal-agent/](../agents/dw-paralegal-agent/) |\n    69→| `dw-marketer-agent` | `marketer_request` | [agents/dw-marketer-agent/](../agents/dw-marketer-agent/) |\n    70→| `dw-accountant-agent` | `accountant_request` | [agents/dw-accountant-agent/](../agents/dw-accountant-agent/) |\n    71→\n    72→## Request Flow\n    73→\n    74→```\n    75→AugLoop                          OfficeAgent Container\n    76→───────                          ─────────────────────\n    77→   │\n    78→   │  SessionInit { agentId: \"workspace-agent\" }\n    79→   ├──────────────────────────────────▶ SessionInitHandler\n    80→   │                                          │"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VcS2pjCQDmBrQu85ZKAMvr","session_id":"059c34c4-4758-4e2f-87ba-9357713e7c91","uuid":"2afde5fe-82a2-4336-85f5-40e84d783875"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SkBjAVxzLkNk9udf3vbRwh","type":"tool_result","content":"import { BaseAgent, SessionContext, AgentWorkspaceManager, logInfo, logDebug, logError, HookRegistry, createAgentHooks, mergeHooks, TurnContext, wsManager, OfficeAgentSettingsManager } from '@officeagent/core';\nimport WebSocket from 'ws';\nimport { registerExcelHeadlessHandlers } from './handlers/excel-headless';\nimport { disableRetries } from '@officeagent/excel-headless';\nimport claude, { Options } from '@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk';\nimport {\n    MessageType,\n    RequestContext,\n    AgentRequestMessage,\n    JsonRpcMethod,\n    SydneyMessage,\n    QueryErrorCode,\n    AgentState,\n} from '@officeagent/message-protocol';\nimport { join } from 'path';\nimport ejs from 'ejs';\nimport { readFile, writeFile, readdir, stat, mkdir } from 'fs/promises';\nimport {\n    FileWatcherService,\n    WebSocketMessengerService,\n    ClaudeMessageLoggerService,\n    DebugZipCreatorService,\n    StateZipCreatorService,\n    QueryInterruptManager,\n    ExternalDocumentTracker,\n    RequestInterceptors,\n    AgentStateManager,\n} from './services';\nimport { initPerfTracking, createPerfTrackingHooks, trackMessage, flushPerfLog } from './services/performance-tracker-service';\nimport { initChainOfThought, trackChainOfThought, closeChainOfThought, createSubAgentCOTHooks, ChainOfThoughtFlights, summarizeResultMessage, shouldShowCOTForRequestInterceptionFlow, isChainOfThoughtDisplayed } from '@officeagent/chain-of-thought';\nimport { agentRegistry } from './registry';\nimport { handleExcelDownload } from './services/excel/dev/download-handler';\nimport { BaseHooksProvider, WordHooksProvider, ExcelHooksProvider, PowerPointHooksProvider } from './hooks';\nimport { AgentType, GeneratedFileInfo, ExternalDocumentInfo, DocumentGenerationCallbacks } from './types';\nimport { ChatHistoryService } from './services/chat-history-service';\nimport { sendTaskCompletionNotification, sendOfficeAgentChatMessage, sendArtifactGenerationNotification, sendChatResponseAck } from './utils';\nimport { ENABLE_JSON_RPC_FLIGHT, ENABLE_SONNET_LANGUAGE_DETECTION_FLIGHT, ARTIFACT_TYPE_DOCX, ARTIFACT_TYPE_PPTX, ARTIFACT_TYPE_XLSX } from './constants';\nimport { isFileObserverFeatureEnabled } from './hooks/file-observer-hooks';\nimport { FileEventObserver } from './services/file-event-observer';\nimport { AgentRequestHandler } from './handlers/agent-request-handler';\nimport { AgentStateService } from './services/agent-state-service';\nimport { existsSync } from 'fs';\nimport { QueryClassifier } from './sidecar/query-classifier/main';\nimport { areRequestInterceptorsEnabled } from './services/request-interceptors/request-interceptors';\nimport { parseGroundingContent } from '@officeagent/grounding';\nimport { ConversationExpiredError } from './errors';\nimport { RuntimeAgentConfigStore } from './services/runtime-agent-config-store';\nimport { refreshMetadataFromDisk } from './services/excel/excel-file-metadata';\n\nexport class CreateAgent extends BaseAgent {\n    private queryInterruptManager = new QueryInterruptManager();\n    private externalDocTracker = new ExternalDocumentTracker();\n    private context?: SessionContext;\n    private generatedFileInfo?: GeneratedFileInfo;\n    private wordPageBreakDisabled = false; // Cache feature gate setting for Word page breaks\n    private useOoxmlCsharp = false; // Cache feature gate setting for C# OOXML document creation\n    private jsonRpcEnabled = false; // Cache JSON-RPC flight setting\n    private hookRegistry: HookRegistry; // Agent-specific hooks registry\n    private chatHistoryService = new ChatHistoryService();\n    private agentStateService = new AgentStateService();\n    private requestInterceptors: RequestInterceptors | undefined;\n    private agentRequestHandler?: AgentRequestHandler;\n\n    private wereRequestInterceptorsEngaged: boolean = false;\n    private disableRequestInterceptorsForCurrentConversation: boolean = false; // Flag to disable request interceptors for the current conversation after the claude engagement.\n\n    private static readonly DEFAULT_OFFICE_AGENT_CAPABILITIES = 'You are Office Agent, an assistant built and operated by Microsoft that is the world\\'s foremost expert in document creation and research, specializing in generating high-quality Word, Excel, and PowerPoint documents using specialized skills and tools.';\n\n    private static readonly DEFAULT_CONTEXT_READING_INSTRUCTIONS = 'No previous context. Skip this step and move to the next step.';\n\n    public constructor() {\n        super(agentRegistry);\n\n        // Initialize hook registry and register hooks\n        this.hookRegistry = new HookRegistry();\n\n        // Register base hooks shared by all agents (performance tracking, CoT)\n        this.hookRegistry.register('base', new BaseHooksProvider());\n\n        // Register agent-specific hooks\n        this.hookRegistry.register(AgentType.WordAgent, new WordHooksProvider());\n        this.hookRegistry.register(AgentType.ExcelAgent, new ExcelHooksProvider());\n        this.hookRegistry.register(AgentType.PowerPointAgent, new PowerPointHooksProvider());\n    }\n\n    public getGeneratedFileInfo(): GeneratedFileInfo | undefined {\n        return this.generatedFileInfo;\n    }\n\n    public hasExternalDocumentCreated(): boolean {\n        return this.externalDocTracker.wasCompleted();\n    }\n\n    public async initialize(context: SessionContext): Promise<void> {\n        logInfo(0x1e0dc656 /* tag_4d2zw */, 'Initializing Create Agent...');\n\n        if (context.settingsManager?.changeGate('changeGateSanityTest')) {\n            logInfo(0x1e0dc655 /* tag_4d2zv */, '✅ Change gate \"changeGateSanityTest\" is enabled');\n        } else {\n            logInfo(0x1e0dc654 /* tag_4d2zu */, '❌ Change gate \"changeGateSanityTest\" is disabled');","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VcS2pjCQDmBrQu85ZKAMvr","session_id":"059c34c4-4758-4e2f-87ba-9357713e7c91","uuid":"96493807-a026-4990-ad0c-04ed77972011"}
